      "id": "PopularPost262411",
      "post_content": "[Hurkyl's Recall](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hurkyl's Recall) is a versatile spell. For what it does, it is extremely undercosted, and if that isn't good enough, it's an instant on top of that. You can use it in a number of ways - offensively, if the battlefield is clogged up with your opponent's artifacts; defensively, if you want to protect your artifacts from targeted destruction (or even your own [Wrath of God](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God) type effect); or as a way to replenish your hand to fuel storm or re-use artifacts with \"comes onto the battlefield\" abilities. But in reference to the flavor text... exactly what has Drafna ever been credited with except for Drafna's Restoration?",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost262411\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hurkyl's Recall\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hurkyl's Recall\">Hurkyl's Recall</a> is a versatile spell.  For what it does, it is extremely undercosted, and if that isn't good enough, it's an instant on top of that.  You can use it in a number of ways - offensively, if the battlefield is clogged up with your opponent's artifacts; defensively, if you want to protect your artifacts from targeted destruction (or even your own <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wrath of God\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God\">Wrath of God</a> type effect); or as a way to replenish your hand to fuel storm or re-use artifacts with \"comes onto the battlefield\" abilities.  But in reference to the flavor text... exactly what has Drafna ever been credited with except for Drafna's Restoration?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '262411'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (8/14/2012 5:33:55 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    R